entry.title: Euryomyrtus ramosissima subsp. prostrata
entry.content: Tiny prostate plant with tiny flowers (about 7-8mm diam) which face downwards. Woody stem. Observed Sept to Nov.

entry.title: Daviesia arenaria
entry.content: Daviesia arenaria because of the colour of the flower and the ‘folded’ phyllodes.

entry.title: Stylidium calcaratum spp. agg.
entry.content: White form also observed in the general area.
